HEADWORD: Luny
<hw>Lu"ny</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Shortened fr.
<ets>lunatic</ets>.]</ety> <def>Crazy; insane; mentally unsound.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>loony</asp> and <asp>looney</asp>.]</altsp>
<mark>[Low, U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
